<item>
            <title>[GROOVY-9855] Compiler does not resolve compile-time constants in string concatenation</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/GROOVY-9855</link>
                <project id="12318123" key="GROOVY">Groovy</project>
                    <description>&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-groovy&quot;&gt;
@Qualifier(ConfigProps.PREFIX + &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos;.suffix&apos;&lt;/span&gt;)
@CompileStatic
&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;class &lt;/span&gt;ConfigProps {
    public static final &lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;String&lt;/span&gt; PREFIX = &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos;prefix&apos;&lt;/span&gt;
}
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;In this case, the value (&lt;tt&gt;prefix.suffix&lt;/tt&gt;) is a compile-time constant and should be available as an annotation parameter, but the compiler does not recognize this. Both plain and static compilation produce errors, though different errors:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;dynamic:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
The value &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;for&lt;/span&gt; annotation attribute Qualifier.value must be a constant expression
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;static:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
Attribute &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos;value&apos;&lt;/span&gt; should have type &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos;java.lang.&lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;String&lt;/span&gt;&apos;&lt;/span&gt;; but found type &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos;java.lang.&lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;Object&lt;/span&gt;&apos;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
